[
  {
    "startTime": 0.266,
    "endTime": 1.668,
    "text": "And I now I thought I'd share some of my favorite"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.668,
    "endTime": 2.902,
    "text": "\"worst first date\" stories from you guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.902,
    "endTime": 7.307,
    "text": "This first one's from @jordancohen2u."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.307,
    "endTime": 9.75,
    "text": "She says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.8,
    "endTime": 13.0,
    "text": "I was really into this guy, but I was so nervous on our first date that when he told me, \"You smell good,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.0,
    "endTime": 15.0,
    "text": "I replied, \"Thanks, I use both of my nostrils.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.552,
    "endTime": 23.156,
    "text": "This one's from @annabanana0626."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.156,
    "endTime": 25.625,
    "text": "She says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.7,
    "endTime": 28.0,
    "text": "I was walking ahead of him and got into the car parked out front before he could open the door for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.0,
    "endTime": 31.0,
    "text": "He knocked on the window and yelled through the glass, \"This isn't my car!\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.932,
    "endTime": 34.934000000000005,
    "text": "\"It's a Mercedes Benz. I kind of like it.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.934,
    "endTime": 37.169,
    "text": "\"Whose car is this?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.17,
    "endTime": 39.105000000000004,
    "text": "I'll wait."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.105,
    "endTime": 43.208,
    "text": "This one's from @foreversmiling2."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.209,
    "endTime": 45.578,
    "text": "She says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.6,
    "endTime": 50.0,
    "text": "On my first date, and my first time at a sushi place, I decided to order thirteen rolls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.0,
    "endTime": 55.0,
    "text": "I thought \"rolls\" meant individual pieces of sushi. The servers had to push two tables together just to hold them all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.57,
    "endTime": 59.92,
    "text": "\"13 rolls of sushi.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.92,
    "endTime": 60.96,
    "text": "\"Well, whatever you say."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.96,
    "endTime": 62.896,
    "text": "Bring 'em -- keep bringing 'em.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.896,
    "endTime": 66.533,
    "text": "\"I've been here before.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.533,
    "endTime": 69.869,
    "text": "This one's from @snookicookie16."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.869,
    "endTime": 72.672,
    "text": "She says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.7,
    "endTime": 75.0,
    "text": "At the end of the night, he acted like he was going in for a kiss,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.0,
    "endTime": 78.0,
    "text": "then put his whole mouth over my nose and blew into it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.0,
    "endTime": 82.0,
    "text": "He laughed and said he does it to his dogs and calls it a \"puppy trumpet.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.25,
    "endTime": 85.819,
    "text": "Puppy trumpet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.819,
    "endTime": 88.88,
    "text": "Puppy trumpet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.189,
    "endTime": 91.157,
    "text": "What a garbage person."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.561,
    "endTime": 96.83000000000001,
    "text": "It's my puppy trumpet, man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.83,
    "endTime": 99.132,
    "text": "It said the end of the night,  at the end of the date,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.132,
    "endTime": 103.10300000000001,
    "text": "it was the ol' puppy trumpet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.103,
    "endTime": 106.705,
    "text": "This one's from @Hotovy. Hotovy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.706,
    "endTime": 108.308,
    "text": "He says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.4,
    "endTime": 112.0,
    "text": "The first time I met my wife, she was convinced there were 52 states in the U.S."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.0,
    "endTime": 118.0,
    "text": "When I suggested there were only 50 states, she called her brother, who confirmed that there were in fact 52 states."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.221,
    "endTime": 124.257,
    "text": "- Never gonna win. - They're married!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.257,
    "endTime": 126.126,
    "text": "-You're never gonna win, dude. -He's married."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.126,
    "endTime": 128.19400000000002,
    "text": "-He learned his lesson early. -Exactly, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.193,
    "endTime": 132.298,
    "text": "This one's from @PatrickAH81."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.298,
    "endTime": 133.8,
    "text": "He says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.9,
    "endTime": 136.0,
    "text": "I once spilled soda on my crotch while pulling into my date's driveway."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.0,
    "endTime": 139.0,
    "text": "My first words when she answered the door were, \"It's not pee.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.176,
    "endTime": 144.677,
    "text": "I'm clean. It's not pee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.677,
    "endTime": 146.912,
    "text": "- Yeah, not pee. - All right, well, what is it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.913,
    "endTime": 148.41400000000002,
    "text": "It's a little bit of poop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.849,
    "endTime": 152.584,
    "text": "This one's from @lindachilders1."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.585,
    "endTime": 154.154,
    "text": "She said..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.2,
    "endTime": 156.0,
    "text": "A friend once set me up on a blind date."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.0,
    "endTime": 158.0,
    "text": "I wasn't in a great mood because I had received a traffic ticket a few hours before."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.0,
    "endTime": 162.0,
    "text": "My day got worse when my blind date turned out to be the cop who gave me the ticket."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.228,
    "endTime": 163.89700000000002,
    "text": "-Oh! -What!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.897,
    "endTime": 167.367,
    "text": "I know you! That's fate!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.367,
    "endTime": 168.434,
    "text": "That's fate!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.434,
    "endTime": 169.835,
    "text": "Oh, my goodness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.836,
    "endTime": 172.33800000000002,
    "text": "This one's from @Mfonda."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.338,
    "endTime": 173.84,
    "text": "She says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.9,
    "endTime": 177.0,
    "text": "On our first date, the guy choked on an omelet and blew an onion out of his nose."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.13,
    "endTime": 182.94899999999998,
    "text": "He could have used the puppy trumpet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.17,
    "endTime": 185.218,
    "text": "That's what you use it for, man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.218,
    "endTime": 186.319,
    "text": "Yeah, that's what you got to get there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.319,
    "endTime": 188.11999999999998,
    "text": "That's what you use it for, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.121,
    "endTime": 192.258,
    "text": "Next one is from our very own Questlove."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.3,
    "endTime": 198.89800000000002,
    "text": "This is very interesting here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.898,
    "endTime": 200.5,
    "text": "He says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.6,
    "endTime": 205.0,
    "text": "I had dinner with Rosario Dawson, and let Mos Def and his bros crash the party."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.0,
    "endTime": 208.0,
    "text": "Mos casually order her a $500 birthday cake. It wasn't her birthday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.0,
    "endTime": 213.0,
    "text": "The bill came to $1400. I didn't have $1400."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.15,
    "endTime": 218.984,
    "text": "That was it? That was it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.985,
    "endTime": 219.65200000000002,
    "text": "That was it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.652,
    "endTime": 221.72,
    "text": "There's only 280 characters. I couldn't go on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.721,
    "endTime": 227.594,
    "text": "Have you ever tried to go on a second date, or no?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.594,
    "endTime": 229.495,
    "text": "I didn't get a second date, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.29,
    "endTime": 233.233,
    "text": "Rosario -- we got to bring this up when she comes on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.702,
    "endTime": 237.303,
    "text": "That's the greatest --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.303,
    "endTime": 239.739,
    "text": "Tariq, you have a worst first date story?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.739,
    "endTime": 243.309,
    "text": "No, all my first dates, they went swimmingly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.745,
    "endTime": 248.848,
    "text": "-Swimmingly -- swimmingly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.848,
    "endTime": 255.58800000000002,
    "text": "Last one here is from @ash10g."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.588,
    "endTime": 257.49,
    "text": "She says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.5,
    "endTime": 259.0,
    "text": "We had a mini makeout, then he fist bumped me and said, \"Nice work.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.959,
    "endTime": 261.693,
    "text": "There you have it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.694,
    "endTime": 263.329,
